time complexity: O(n)
space complexity: O(n)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: Dynamic programming is used to track the number of valid sequences for Bob. The dp array stores the count of valid sequences ending at each character. The final result is computed by comparing the total scores of Alice and Bob.
